These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-8-1::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: ice-hockey, lacrosse, badminton
1. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the far right##1
2. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is not to the left of the person who's sport is lacrosse##8
3. the person who's sport is badminton is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is lacrosse##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |    2    |    3     |
| Sport   | badminton | lacrosse | ice-hockey |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-8-2::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: puzzles, board-games, filmmaking
1. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is not to the left of the person who's hobby is puzzles##8
2. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1   |   2    |     3     |
| Hobby   | puzzles | filmmaking | board-games |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-8-3::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: coffee, iced-tea, sprite
1. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
2. the person drinking coffee is not to the right of the person drinking sprite##8

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2   |  3  |
| Beverage   | iced-tea | coffee | sprite |

 #################################

 
