.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-8-5::.
There are 3 different nationalities: nigerian, british, japanese
1. the british is in an even position##4
2. the british is not to the right of the japanese##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |     3     |
| Nationality   | nigerian | british | japanese |

