.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-8-9::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: juice, hot-chocolate, soy-milk
1. the person drinking soy-milk is not to the left of the person drinking juice##8
2. the person drinking juice is between the person drinking hot-chocolate and the person drinking soy-milk##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2   |  3   |
